{
  "text": "The Unrelated Parallel Machine Scheduling Problem with Sequence and Machine Dependent Setup Time represents one of the classes derived from the PMSP. In such a case, there is a set N = {1, ..., n} of n tasks and a set M = {1, ..., m} of m unrelated machines (m < n), with the following characteristics [CITATION_1] :",
